FIELD NAME / NOM DU CHAMP: CSD Code / Code de la SDR 1981
ENGLISH DEFINITION / DÉFINITION ANGLAISE: Unique 7-digit code identifying each Census subdivision (CSD) in the 1981 CWB file and linking it to its 1986 CSD Code
